<plot>Crooner and pianist Gene Austin, band singer Jane Shirley, and his two stooges, Coco &amp; Candy, aren't making any money at their nightclub, so Austin buys a trailer, hooks it to a car, and puts their show on at trailer camps around the country. They meet up with a bunch of kid entertainers, and the combined shows are a hit...on the Trailer Camp Circut.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?452640</url></doc>
